title: Ring of Fire - November 16 2013
description:
November 16, 2013
Ring of Fire 
Hosted by Robert F. Kennedy Jr., Mike Papantonio and Sam Seder


This week on Ring of Fire Radio: Rolling Stone contributing editor Tim Dickinson will tell us how Republicans have rigged the electoral system to the point that they can almost never lose.

Author and historian Rick Perlstein will tell us about the history of Republican extremism.

Author Frank Schaeffer will explain how the Tea PartyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s extreme positions are coming directly from evangelical leaders.

Washington Post columnist Harold Meyerson will tell us about the divide between corporate Democrats and Progressive Democrats.

And author Les Leopold will join us for a discussion on why millionaires and billionaires are getting government handouts, while the needy are having to sacrifice even more.
